INSERT INTO recipes VALUE(1090,"Spicy Bacon &amp; Tomato Brunch","PT30M","PT10M","PT40M","Make and share this Spicy Bacon &amp; Tomato Brunch recipe from Food.com.","Breakfast",2.0,1.0,95.2,5.7,1.9,8.2,107.5,9.1,2.0,4.5,3.0,"0.0","Spicy Bacon &amp; Tomato Brunch Recipe Instructions:  1: Cut the bacon into small strips and add to saucepan. 2: Cook over medium heat. 3: Finely chop the onion and garlic; add to saucepan and fry with ginger until soft and translucent (not brown). 4: When vegetables are cooked, open tomatoes and cut into small pieces; add tomatoes and juice to saucepan with salt and pepper. 5: The secret of this recipe is to keep cooking over a medium heat, stirring occasionally, until the tomato juice has reduced to a thickish sauce. 6: When desired thickness is reached, serve on toast -- it certainly wakes those taste buds up.");
